document_data.name: Jeyrelle Fey
document_data.mainbody: '''Jeyrelle Fey''' was one of the few female members of [[Bregan D'aerthe]] in the early 15{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Description: Jeyrelle was a beautiful woman with amber eyes.
document_data.Skills: She was a priestess of an unknown goddess that was not [[Lolth]].
document_data.History:
In [[1488 DR]], Jeyrelle, together with [[Braelin Janquay]], acted as support for the resurrected [[Zaknafein]] for a mission for Bregan D'aerthe.

At Bregan D'aerthe's meeting with [[House Hunzrin]] in [[Waterdeep]]'s sewers, she remained behind.
